Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.29,0:04:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道咲世子那傢伙 連Rounds也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:28.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是魯魯修?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:33.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是 在布里塔尼亞本國
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:34.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是皇子的時候的我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.76,0:04:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦 認錯人了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不過是個庶民
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:41.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
